verbose_text: For instance, the overexpression of hsa-miR-21-5p, one of the best studied miRNAs, not only was suggested to be an important prognostic factor for the overall survival of NSCLC patients [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR] but also was deregulated in other cancers, such as breast cancer and cervical cancer; it seems to be a common oncogenic miRNA of no tissue specificity [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
